### Dashboard Evidence

In Wazuh Dashboard, go to **Security Configuration Assessment** and review passed/failed checks, policy name, endpoint name, and remediation guidance.

### GRC Evidence Statement

Wazuh SCA was used to review endpoint configuration settings. Failed checks were treated as compliance gaps and added to remediation tracking — supporting secure configuration review and audit readiness.

